001
002package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.node;
003
004/**
005 * This enumeration provides a listing of the available kinds of
006 * {@link INodeItem} implementations.
007 */
008public enum NodeItemKind {
009  /**
010   * An {@link INodeItem} based on a Metaschema (@link {@link IModuleNodeItem}}).
011   */
012  METASCHEMA,
013  /**
014   * An {@link INodeItem} based on data represented using a Metaschema-based model
015   * (@link {@link IDocumentNodeItem}}).
016   */
017  DOCUMENT,
018  ASSEMBLY,
019  FIELD,
020  FLAG;
021}
